    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>这是一部可以玩的轻推理群像剧视觉小说系列作品！</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063530/extras/dc0d206efef19b410402771153cc834d.poster.avif?t=1772121605\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063530/extras/dc0d206efef19b410402771153cc834d.webm?t=1772121605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063530/extras/dc0d206efef19b410402771153cc834d.mp4?t=1772121605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到神秘的加拿大侦探大赛现场！在这里，你需要策略使用队友的探案法收集证据，审问嫌疑人和找出真相！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >正式版本将包含6大档案，其中包含来自加拿大最狡猾的策划者设计的错综复杂的谜题。每个档案通关需要 2-4 小时完成，具体时间取决于作为玩家的你的推理技巧……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >好了，现在...该你上场了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >爱你们的，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏主持人</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063530/extras/d64be8e7405f7a20f0c5fd0c06db209c.avif?t=1772121605\" width=620 height=149 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >用五种不同的探案法来解开谜题</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063530/extras/51f5e617753d7daba986c9c1d53894ff.poster.avif?t=1772121605\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063530/extras/51f5e617753d7daba986c9c1d53894ff.webm?t=1772121605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.stea